OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FThere were multiple breaches by PSNI
OL,7,Fofficers in the duty of care offered
OL,8,Fto a vulnerable teenager who was later
OL,9,Fknocked down and killed in Co Antrim
OL,10,Fin 2018, a Police Ombudsman
OL,11,Finvestigation has found.
OL,13,FThe ombudsman's office has recommended
OL,14,Fa new policy be put in place between
OL,15,Fthe force and the Northern Ireland
OL,16,FAmbulance Service (NIAS) to deal with
OL,17,Fpeople who are intoxicated and refuse
OL,18,Fmedical treatment.
