OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FShannon McQuillan, a 19-year-old law
OL,7,Fstudent, and her 21-year-old
OL,8,Fboyfriend, Owen McFerran, were both
OL,9,Fhit by a van after three PSNI
OL,10,Fofficers, a paramedic and a trainee
OL,11,Femergency technician left them alone
OL,12,Fat a bus shelter on the Moneynick Road
OL,13,Fin Magherafelt in the early hours of
OL,14,FJanuary 20, 2018.
OL,16,FMs McQuillan was killed and Mr
OL,17,FMcFerran sustained life-changing
OL,18,Finjuries in the collision which
OL,19,Foccurred at 3.40am.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/19
