OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FThe investigation found the Ambulance
OL,7,FService and PSNI had first encountered
OL,8,FMs McQuillan and Mr McFerran at 2am in
OL,9,Fa car park in Magherafelt, where Ms
OL,10,FMcQuillan was found to be unconscious
OL,11,Fafter falling a number of times.
OL,13,FAfter a telephone call was made to Ms
OL,14,FMcQuillan's mother by police, advising
OL,15,Fthat her daughter and boyfriend were
OL,16,Fbeing taken to Antrim Area Hospital,
OL,17,Fofficers left them in the care of two
OL,18,Fambulance staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/19
