OL,6,FHowever, the same officers were called
OL,7,Fback to the car park by ambulance
OL,8,Fpersonnel after Ms McQuillan's
OL,9,Fbehaviour became erratic, the
OL,10,Fombudsman investigation said.
OL,12,FFollowing a discussion between Ms
OL,13,FMcQuillan, ambulance staff and police,
OL,14,Fit was agreed officers would follow
OL,15,Fthe ambulance to a roundabout in
OL,16,FMagherafelt to ensure it proceeded to
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/19
