OL,6,FShortly before 3am, the ambulance
OL,7,Fpulled into a bus layby on the
OL,8,FMoneynick Road, and staff onboard
OL,9,Fcalled for police assistance again
OL,10,Ffollowing concerns about Ms
OL,11,FMcQuillan's behaviour.
OL,13,FTwo different police officers to those
OL,14,Fwho attended earlier arrived at the
OL,15,Flayby at 3am while a third, who was
OL,16,Fmore senior and operating in a
OL,17,Fsupervisory capacity, attended minutes
OL,18,Flater.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/19
