OL,6,FFollowing a discussion between the
OL,7,Fmedical team and PSNI officers, the
OL,8,Fcouple got out of the ambulance and
OL,9,Fwere left, alone, at a bus shelter on
OL,10,Fthe Moneynick Road.
OL,12,FAt 3.38am the police received the
OL,13,Ffirst of three phone calls about two
OL,14,Fpeople walking in the middle of the
OL,15,FMoneynick Road and two minutes later a
OL,16,Fmotorist informed police he had
OL,17,Fcollided with two people on the same
OL,18,Froad.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/19
