OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FPolice attended along with other
OL,7,Femergency services, but Ms McQuillan
OL,8,Fdied at the scene while Mr McFerran
OL,9,Fwas taken to hospital in a critical
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FSubsequent tests established that both
OL,13,Fhad high levels of alcohol in their
OL,14,Fblood at the time.
OL,16,FOmbudsman investigators highlighted
OL,17,Fthis was significant information when
OL,18,Fit came to how officers assessed the
OL,19,Fvulnerability and risk of Ms McQuillan
OL,20,Fand Mr McFerran.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/19
