OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FThe Police Ombudsman investigation
OL,7,Ffound that Ms McQuillan had fallen and
OL,8,Fhit her head a number of times before
OL,9,Fshe came into contact with police and
OL,10,Fambulance personnel in Magherafelt and
OL,11,Falso had visible injuries to her leg.
OL,13,FThe two ambulance staff told ombudsman
OL,14,Finvestigators that they had stopped
OL,15,Ftheir vehicle in the layby and asked
OL,16,Ffor police assistance because Ms
OL,17,FMcQuillan had become aggressive
OL,18,Ftowards them and Mr McFerran, and had
OL,19,Falso tried to harm herself.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/19
