OL,6,FThe investigation said the accounts of
OL,7,Fpolice and NIAS staff who attended at
OL,8,Fthe Moneynick Road were found to be
OL,9,Finconsistent.
OL,11,FThe ombudsman concluded that the
OL,12,Fcommunication between the police
OL,13,Fofficers in attendance at the
OL,14,FMoneynick Road and the NIAS staff had
OL,15,Fbeen "wholly inadequate".
OL,17,FThis also led to a separate PSNI
OL,18,Finvestigation into the conduct of NIAS
OL,19,Fstaff.
