OL,6,FA police file was submitted to the
OL,7,FPublic Prosecution Service (PPS) but
OL,8,Fit decided that no criminal charges
OL,9,Fshould be brought against any of the
OL,10,Fparamedics at the scene.
OL,12,FThe ombudsman investigation found that
OL,13,Fthere had been "multiple breaches in
OL,14,Fthe duty of care offered" to Ms
OL,15,FMcQuillan and Mr McFerran by police
OL,16,Fofficers.
OL,26,@uD@POUvD@YO]
