OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FThese included failing to complete
OL,7,Feven the most basic checks in relation
OL,8,Fto them, failing to recognise the
OL,9,Fvulnerability and risks of leaving the
OL,10,Ftwo alone together beside a road and
OL,11,Ffailing to safeguard the couple's
OL,12,Fwelfare.
OL,14,FThe Police Ombudsman's Office
OL,15,Fsubmitted a file to the PPS relating
OL,16,Fto the three police officers who
OL,17,Fattended at Moneynick Road for the
OL,18,Fpotential offences of gross negligence
OL,19,Fmanslaughter and misconduct in public
OL,20,Foffice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/19
