OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,FThe PPS directed that none of the
OL,7,Fpolice officers should be prosecuted.
OL,9,FMs McQuillan's family requested a
OL,10,Freview of this decision and in January
OL,11,F2021, the PPS advised the Police
OL,12,FOmbudsman that the outcome was no
OL,13,Fprosecution.
OL,15,FSubsequent PSNI misconduct proceedings
OL,16,Ffound that the conduct of two of the
OL,17,Fthree officers who had attended the
OL,18,Fambulance amounted to gross misconduct.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/19
