OL,6,FThe ombudsman also recommended that a
OL,7,Fnew policy be put in place between the
OL,8,FPSNI and NIAS for dealing with people
OL,9,Fwho are intoxicated and refuse medical
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,FThe Police Ombudsman's Chief
OL,13,FExecutive, Hugh Hume, said: "More
OL,14,Fshould have been done in this case to
OL,15,Fprotect the extremely vulnerable young
OL,16,Fwoman and man from harm.
OL,26,@uD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/19
