SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1754579490
OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,F"The police response was wholly
OL,7,Finadequate, and a police misconduct
OL,8,Fpanel supported the ombudsman's
OL,9,Fevidence that there had been a failure
OL,10,Fof professional duty.
OL,12,F"Safeguarding vulnerable people in an
OL,13,Foperational environment is an
OL,14,Fimportant and frequent role for first
OL,15,Fresponders. Ineffective or ill-
OL,16,Finformed decisions can, as in this
OL,17,Fcase, have dreadful and far-reaching
OL,18,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/19
