OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1754579490
OL,3,CEmergency services failings found over
OL,4,Cdeath of student
OL,6,F"It is therefore essential that police
OL,7,Fofficers and all frontline partners
OL,8,Fwork together smoothly and efficiently
OL,9,Fto minimise the risk to those whose
OL,10,Fjudgment and health appears impaired."
OL,12,FMr Hume added: "This tragic case
OL,13,Ftherefore demonstrates the absolute
OL,14,Fneed for effective and well understood
OL,15,Fjoint protocols between the PSNI and
OL,16,Fthe NIAS to deal with such
OL,17,Fcircumstances.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]tD@POU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/19
