OL,6,F"We also recognise the impact that
OL,7,Fthis incident had and continues to
OL,8,Fhave on our officers and their
OL,9,Ffamilies.
OL,11,F"We accept that more could and should
OL,12,Fhave been done by police to prevent
OL,13,Fthe circumstances that preceded
OL,14,FShannon's death and Owen's injuries.
OL,15,FFor that we are truly sorry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
